To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private KeltnerChannels _kch;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_kch = KCH(symbol, period, k);

// In OnData()
if (_kch.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "middleband", _kch.MiddleBand.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "upperband", _kch.UpperBand.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "lowerband", _kch.LowerBand.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "averagetruerange", _kch.AverageTrueRange.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "keltnerchannels", _kch.Current.Value);
}
